#. @item Indicate the selected color in the swatch book. This symbol should be translated to whatever symbol is most appropriate for вАЬselectedвАЭ in the translation language. Example symbols: вЬУ U+2713 CHECK MARK. вЬЧ U+2717 BALLOT X. вЬШ U+2718 HEAVY BALLOT X. вЧЛ U+25CB WHITE CIRCLE. вЧѓ U+25EF LARGE CIRCLE. Do not use emoji characters as they may render colorful on some systems, so they will ignore the automatically chosen color which is used get best contrast with the background. (Also U+FE0E VARIATION SELECTOR-15 does not prevent colorful rendering.)
#: swatchbook.cpp:103
